  "translations": {
    "en": "Ja'far ibn Muhammad ibn Masrur (may Allah have mercy on him) narrated to us. He said: al-Husayn ibn Muhammad ibn 'Amer narrated to us, from his uncle 'Abdullah ibn 'Amer, from Ibn Abi 'Umayr, from Hamza ibn Humran, from his father, from Abu Hamza, from 'Ali ibn al-Husayn, from his father, from Amir al-Mu'minin (blessings of Allah upon them all),",
    "ur": "جعفر بن محمد بن مسرور (رحمہ اللہ) نے ہم سے بیان کیا،",
    "tr": "Cafer b. Muhammed b. Mesrur (r.a.) bize rivayet etti,",
    "fa": "جعفر بن محمد بن مسرور (رحمه الله) برای ما نقل کرد،",
    "id": "Ja'far bin Muhammad bin Masrur menceritakan kepada kami,",
    "bn": "জাফর ইবনে মুহাম্মাদ ইবনে মাসরুর (রহ.) আমাদের বর্ণনা করেছেন،",
    "es": "Ja'far ibn Muhammad ibn Masrur nos narró,",
    "fr": "Ja'far ibn Muhammad ibn Masrur nous a rapporté,",
    "de": "Ja'far ibn Muhammad ibn Masrur berichtete uns,",
    "ru": "Джафар ибн Мухаммад ибн Масрур рассказал нам,",
    "zh": "贾法尔·本·穆罕默德·本·马斯鲁尔向我们讲述了，"
